# M365 Email Hermes Plugin Environment Template

Copy this file to `.env` and fill in your credentials.

## Required
M365_MAIL_CLIENT_ID=
M365_MAIL_CLIENT_SECRET=
M365_MAIL_TENANT_ID=

## Optional
M365_MAILBOX_USER=user@example.org
EMAIL_ALLOWED_USERS=
M365_ATTACHMENT_MAX_BYTES=10485760
M365_EMAIL_STATE_PATH=.runtime/poll-state.json
M365_POLL_INTERVAL_SECONDS=30
